text:
Hi all!

Just going to clear up some questions for tomorrow.

1. We are going to hike up *Stone Mountain the “Walk-Up Trail.*” It is only 1 mile and *parking lot* is *adjacent to Confederate Hall*. No dogs allowed, but feel free to bring friends and spouses. 
2. We will meet at *12:00PM at the parking lot.*
3. The hike depending on people’s skill levels should be 30-60 minutes. 
4. Let’s plan to *drive to Food Terminal around 1:30PM-2:00PM*. 
5. Food terminal doesn’t take reservations for Sunday so we are going to wing it. 
6. Food terminal address: *Food Terminal, 5000 Buford Hwy NE, Chamblee, GA 30341* (22 minutes away from Stone mountain trail) 
7. If you have any questions, please add yourself to the whatssap group (<https://chat.whatsapp.com/CRF36GRc5AWBjDW0GsBCyq>) or text me ahead of time <tel:3476108030|347-610-8030> if you need information. I probably won’t be looking at my phone around 12:15-12:20PM once majority of people are around. 
For those who need rides, <@U02BQJX5TB8> <@U04184BSKM3> please make sure you know who you are going with and let me know. --> I’m going to assume <@U041PH0B1DF> is taking you guys but also <@U04185JLG8M> lives in West Midtown and maybe closer. I think <@U8QDSG1G9> is picking me up? So we should be all set with drivers <@U03UM07E4D8> and <@UMQUVR2VD>. Maybe if drivers up get tired of driving we can switch drivers for bringing us back home haha.

Okay if anything else is unclear, let me know,
Cherie Lum
